This Software provides a basic stateful IRC bot written in the spare
time of a broke and bored college Student. Keep that in mind as you
poke around my code. I am open for pointers and suggestion.

Current Commands:

  Priviledged (the user issuing the command is a part of authorized nick list)

    join channel <key>
      joins a channel and uses the optional key if provided

    put <string>
      appends a string to the buffer saved in the bot's state

    show
      outputs the current buffer saved in state to the current channel

    delete
      delete the contents of said stored buffer

    addMaster nick
      adds a nick to the set of known masters

  UnPriviledged (Anyone)

    help
      display some help information
